#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn44.6"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn44.6:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 44 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 44 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Abyākatavagga "
msgstr "1. The Undeclared Points "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 6. Catutthasāriputtakoṭṭhikasutta → ārāmasuttaṃ (bj) | sāriputta-koṭṭhiko 4 (or ārāma) (pts1)
msgctxt "sn44.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Catutthasāriputtakoṭṭhikasutta "
msgstr "6. With Sāriputta and Koṭṭhita (4th) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn44.6:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā ca sāriputto, āyasmā ca mahākoṭṭhiko bārāṇasiyaṃ viharanti isipatane migadāye. "
msgstr "At one time Venerable Sāriputta and Venerable Mahākoṭṭhita were staying near Benares, in the deer park at Isipatana. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.6:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yenāyasmā mahākoṭṭhiko tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā mahākoṭṭhikena saddhiṃ sammodi. "
msgstr "Then in the late afternoon, Venerable Sāriputta came out of retreat, went to Venerable Mahākoṭṭhita, and they greeted each other. "

msgctxt "sn44.6:1.3"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā sāriputto āyasmantaṃ mahākoṭṭhikaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one side and said to Mahākoṭṭhita: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.6:1.4"
msgid "“‘kiṃ nu kho, āvuso koṭṭhika, hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’ti … pe … "
msgstr "“Reverend Koṭṭhita, does a Realized One exist after death?” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.6:1.5"
msgid "‘kiṃ panāvuso, neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’ti iti puṭṭho samāno: "
msgstr "“Reverend, when asked these questions, you say that this has not been declared by the Buddha. "

msgctxt "sn44.6:1.6"
msgid "‘etampi kho, āvuso, abyākataṃ bhagavatā—"
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn44.6:1.7"
msgid "neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’ti vadesi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn44.6:1.8"
msgid "Ko nu kho, āvuso, hetu, ko paccayo, yenetaṃ abyākataṃ bhagavatā”ti? "
msgstr "What’s the cause, what’s the reason why this has not been declared by the Buddha?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.389, sc2
msgctxt "sn44.6:2.1"
msgid "“Rūpārāmassa kho, āvuso, rūparatassa rūpasammuditassa rūpanirodhaṃ ajānato apassato yathābhūtaṃ, ‘hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa hoti; "
msgstr "“Reverend, if you like, love, and enjoy form, and don’t truly see the cessation of form, you think ‘a Realized One exists after death’ or "

msgctxt "sn44.6:2.2"
msgid "‘na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa hoti; "
msgstr "‘a Realized One doesn’t exist after death’ or "

msgctxt "sn44.6:2.3"
msgid "‘hoti ca na ca hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa hoti; "
msgstr "‘a Realized One both exists and doesn’t exist after death’ or "

msgctxt "sn44.6:2.4"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa hoti. "
msgstr "‘a Realized One neither exists nor doesn’t exist after death.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.6:2.5"
msgid "Vedanārāmassa kho, āvuso, vedanāratassa vedanāsammuditassa, vedanānirodhaṃ ajānato apassato yathābhūtaṃ, ‘hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa hoti … pe … "
msgstr "If you like, love, and enjoy feeling … "

msgctxt "sn44.6:2.6"
msgid "saññārāmassa kho, āvuso … pe … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn44.6:2.7"
msgid "saṅkhārārāmassa kho āvuso … pe … "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn44.6:2.8"
msgid "viññāṇārāmassa kho, āvuso, viññāṇaratassa viññāṇasammuditassa viññāṇanirodhaṃ ajānato apassato yathābhūtaṃ, ‘hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa hoti … pe … "
msgstr "consciousness, and don’t truly see the cessation of consciousness, you think ‘a Realized One exists after death’ … "

msgctxt "sn44.6:2.9"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa hoti. "
msgstr "‘a Realized One neither exists nor doesn’t exist after death.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn44.6:3.1"
msgid "Na rūpārāmassa kho, āvuso, na rūparatassa na rūpasammuditassa, rūpanirodhaṃ jānato passato yathābhūtaṃ, ‘hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa na hoti … pe … "
msgstr "If you don’t like, love, and enjoy form … "

msgctxt "sn44.6:3.2"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa na hoti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn44.6:3.3"
msgid "Na vedanārāmassa kho, āvuso … pe … "
msgstr "feeling … "

msgctxt "sn44.6:3.4"
msgid "na saññārāmassa kho, āvuso … pe … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn44.6:3.5"
msgid "na saṅkhārārāmassa kho, āvuso … pe … "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn44.6:3.6"
msgid "na viññāṇārāmassa kho, āvuso, na viññāṇaratassa na viññāṇasammuditassa, viññāṇanirodhaṃ jānato passato yathābhūtaṃ, ‘hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa na hoti … pe … "
msgstr "consciousness, and you truly see the cessation of consciousness, you don’t think ‘a Realized One exists after death’ … "

msgctxt "sn44.6:3.7"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa na hoti. "
msgstr "‘a Realized One neither exists nor doesn’t exist after death.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.6:3.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, āvuso, hetu, ayaṃ paccayo, yenetaṃ abyākataṃ bhagavatā”ti. "
msgstr "This is the cause, this is the reason why this has not been declared by the Buddha.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.390, sc4
msgctxt "sn44.6:4.1"
msgid "“Siyā panāvuso, aññopi pariyāyo, yenetaṃ abyākataṃ bhagavatā”ti? "
msgstr "“But reverend, could there be another way of explaining why this was not declared by the Buddha?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.6:4.2"
msgid "“Siyā, āvuso. "
msgstr "“There could, reverend. "

msgctxt "sn44.6:4.3"
msgid "Bhavārāmassa kho, āvuso, bhavaratassa bhavasammuditassa, bhavanirodhaṃ ajānato apassato yathābhūtaṃ, ‘hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa hoti … pe … "
msgstr "If you like, love, and enjoy existence, and don’t truly see the cessation of continued existence, you think ‘a Realized One exists after death’ … "

msgctxt "sn44.6:4.4"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa hoti. "
msgstr "‘a Realized One neither exists nor doesn’t exist after death.’ "

msgctxt "sn44.6:4.5"
msgid "Na bhavārāmassa kho, āvuso, na bhavaratassa na bhavasammuditassa, bhavanirodhaṃ jānato passato yathābhūtaṃ, ‘hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa na hoti … pe … "
msgstr "If you don’t like, love, and enjoy existence, and you truly see the cessation of continued existence, you don’t think ‘a Realized One exists after death’ … "

msgctxt "sn44.6:4.6"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa na hoti. "
msgstr "‘a Realized One neither exists nor doesn’t exist after death.’ "

msgctxt "sn44.6:4.7"
msgid "Ayampi kho, āvuso, pariyāyo, yenetaṃ abyākataṃ bhagavatā”ti. "
msgstr "This too is a way of explaining why this was not declared by the Buddha.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn44.6:5.1"
msgid "“Siyā panāvuso, aññopi pariyāyo, yenetaṃ abyākataṃ bhagavatā”ti? "
msgstr "“But reverend, could there be another way of explaining why this was not declared by the Buddha?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.6:5.2"
msgid "“Siyā, āvuso. "
msgstr "“There could, reverend. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.6:5.3"
msgid "Upādānārāmassa kho, āvuso, upādānaratassa upādānasammuditassa, upādānanirodhaṃ ajānato apassato yathābhūtaṃ, ‘hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa hoti … pe … "
msgstr "If you like, love, and enjoy grasping, and don’t truly see the cessation of grasping, you think ‘a Realized One exists after death’ … "

msgctxt "sn44.6:5.4"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa hoti. "
msgstr "‘a Realized One neither exists nor doesn’t exist after death.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.6:5.5"
msgid "Na upādānārāmassa kho, āvuso, na upādānaratassa na upādānasammuditassa, upādānanirodhaṃ jānato passato yathābhūtaṃ, ‘hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa na hoti … pe … "
msgstr "If you don’t like, love, and enjoy grasping, and you truly see the cessation of grasping, you don’t think ‘a Realized One exists after death’ … "

msgctxt "sn44.6:5.6"
msgid "‘neva, hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa na hoti. "
msgstr "‘a Realized One neither exists nor doesn’t exist after death.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.6:5.7"
msgid "Ayampi kho, āvuso, pariyāyo, yenetaṃ abyākataṃ bhagavatā”ti. "
msgstr "This too is a way of explaining why this was not declared by the Buddha.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.391, sc6
msgctxt "sn44.6:6.1"
msgid "“Siyā panāvuso, aññopi pariyāyo, yenetaṃ abyākataṃ bhagavatā”ti? "
msgstr "“But reverend, could there be another way of explaining why this was not declared by the Buddha?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.6:6.2"
msgid "“Siyā, āvuso. "
msgstr "“There could, reverend. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.6:6.3"
msgid "Taṇhārāmassa kho, āvuso, taṇhāratassa taṇhāsammuditassa, taṇhānirodhaṃ ajānato apassato yathābhūtaṃ, ‘hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa hoti … pe … "
msgstr "If you like, love, and enjoy craving, and don’t truly see the cessation of craving, you think ‘a Realized One exists after death’ … "

msgctxt "sn44.6:6.4"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa hoti. "
msgstr "‘a Realized One neither exists nor doesn’t exist after death.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.6:6.5"
msgid "Na taṇhārāmassa kho, āvuso, na taṇhāratassa na taṇhāsammuditassa, taṇhānirodhaṃ jānato passato yathābhūtaṃ, ‘hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa na hoti … pe … "
msgstr "If you don’t like, love, and enjoy craving, and you truly see the cessation of craving, you don’t think ‘a Realized One exists after death’ … "

msgctxt "sn44.6:6.6"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa na hoti. "
msgstr "‘a Realized One neither exists nor doesn’t exist after death.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.6:6.7"
msgid "Ayampi kho, āvuso, pariyāyo, yenetaṃ abyākataṃ bhagavatā”ti. "
msgstr "This too is a way of explaining why this was not declared by the Buddha.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn44.6:7.1"
msgid "“Siyā panāvuso, aññopi pariyāyo, yenetaṃ abyākataṃ bhagavatā”ti? "
msgstr "“But reverend, could there be another way of explaining why this was not declared by the Buddha?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.6:7.2"
msgid "“Ettha dāni, āvuso sāriputta, ito uttari kiṃ icchasi? "
msgstr "“Seriously, reverend, what more could you want? "

#. VAR: vaṭṭaṃ → vattaṃ (s1-3, km, mr) | vaddhaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "sn44.6:7.3"
msgid "Taṇhāsaṅkhayavimuttassa, āvuso sāriputta, bhikkhuno vaṭṭaṃ natthi paññāpanāyā”ti. "
msgstr "For one who is freed due to the ending of craving, there is no cycle of rebirths to be found.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn44.6:7.4"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

